    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. You'll use a Chinese cooking technique known as 'velveting'. It involves cooking meat in egg & cornflour for a moist, silky finish. It sounds challenging, but it's surprisingly simple & makes this chicken stir-fry eggstra special! Under 600 calories.",
